    {
      "id": "E:note:row481041:1",
      "kind": "note_sentence",
      "display": "Ms. [**Known lastname 861**] is a 81 year old woman admitted to T/SICU from the ",
      "code": null,
      "value": null,
      "unit": null,
      "effective": null,
      "source_ref": "note:row481041#s1",
      "text": "Ms. [**Known lastname 861**] is a 81 year old woman admitted to T/SICU from the OR    following a subtotal colectomy with an end ileostomy for bowel    ischemia.    *admitted to [**Hospital1 19**] [**8-5**] for NSTEMI Mi, cath d and angioplasty done of    RCA (had R groin hematoma post procedure)    *on [**8-12**] had rapid afib (rate to 150 s), converted to sinus with    digoxin and then 30 minutes after confusion began complaining of    abdominal pain."
    },
    {
      "id": "E:note:row481041:2",
      "kind": "note_sentence",
      "display": "CT of abdomen done and was concerning for ischemic    bowel.",
      "code": null,
      "value": null,
      "unit": null,
      "effective": null,
      "source_ref": "note:row481041#s2",
      "text": "CT of abdomen done and was concerning for ischemic    bowel."
    },
    {
      "id": "E:note:row481041:3",
      "kind": "note_sentence",
      "display": "To OR for resection.",
      "code": null,
      "value": null,
      "unit": null,
      "effective": null,
      "source_ref": "note:row481041#s3",
      "text": "To OR for resection."
    },
    {
      "id": "E:note:row481041:4",
      "kind": "note_sentence",
      "display": "Postop:    Initially stable then developed rapid afib to 180 with hypotension   ",
      "code": null,
      "value": null,
      "unit": null,
      "effective": null,
      "source_ref": "note:row481041#s4",
      "text": "Postop:    Initially stable then developed rapid afib to 180 with hypotension    [**8-13**], failed electrical cardioversion, cardioverted with amio."
    },
    {
      "id": "E:note:row481041:5",
      "kind": "note_sentence",
      "display": "In and out of afib.",
      "code": null,
      "value": null,
      "unit": null,
      "effective": null,
      "source_ref": "note:row481041#s5",
      "text": "In and out of afib."
    },
    {
      "id": "E:note:row481041:6",
      "kind": "note_sentence",
      "display": "[**Last Name (un) 3864**] placed, bedside echo done.",
      "code": null,
      "value": null,
      "unit": null,
      "effective": null,
      "source_ref": "note:row481041#s6",
      "text": "[**Last Name (un) 3864**] placed, bedside echo done."
    },
    {
      "id": "E:note:row481041:7",
      "kind": "note_sentence",
      "display": "Atrial fibrillation (Afib)    Assessment:    At start of shift was in SR with HR",
      "code": null,
      "value": null,
      "unit": null,
      "effective": null,
      "source_ref": "note:row481041#s7",
      "text": "Atrial fibrillation (Afib)    Assessment:    At start of shift was in SR with HR 60 s."
    },
    {
      "id": "E:note:row481041:8",
      "kind": "note_sentence",
      "display": "SBP 110-120 s.",
      "code": null,
      "value": null,
      "unit": null,
      "effective": null,
      "source_ref": "note:row481041#s8",
      "text": "SBP 110-120 s."
    },
    {
      "id": "E:note:row481041:9",
      "kind": "note_sentence",
      "display": "MAP >60 Amio    drip infusing @ 0.5mg/min.",
      "code": null,
      "value": null,
